message.body: Hi Gabi! Park at chase mill (left before bridge). No time limit
Size B or C nude sheer to waist
Hi Gabi! I can't stop thinking about that chicken last night. It was so yummy and I am really happy I got to eat it with you!! I didn't see the check they gave to Lois...did you ask her?
Likewise! Yea, i was expecting more money because she had told me we were making 5,000 and then told me last night it was 2500

Yes I remember her saying 5k originally which shocked me- seems like a lot. But maybe they cut it when they decided we wouldn't bring our own band? I wasn't involved in find any financial discussions. Good luck today with everything!!!
